                            <comment id="489426" author="adilger" created="Fri, 27 Feb 2026 22:36:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like this patch has significantly increased the duration of recovery-small test_136:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/reports?test_set_script_id=f36cabd0-32c3-11e0-a61c-52540025f9ae&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=d0b69ab2-c341-11e8-a2b9-52540065bddc&amp;amp;source=duration_trend#redirect&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/reports?test_set_script_id=f36cabd0-32c3-11e0-a61c-52540025f9ae&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=d0b69ab2-c341-11e8-a2b9-52540065bddc&amp;amp;source=duration_trend#redirect&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;63214_thumb&quot; href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/attachment/63214/63214_recovery-small-test_136.png&quot; title=&quot;recovery-small-test_136.png&quot; file-preview-type=&quot;image&quot; file-preview-id=&quot;63214&quot; file-preview-title=&quot;recovery-small-test_136.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/thumbnail/63214/_thumb_63214.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It started to show slow test runs before the patch landed (up to 1000s vs. 90s without patch) on 2026-01-07, and then got consistently slow after 2026-02-04 when the patch landed:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/search?client_branch=master&amp;amp;server_branch=master&amp;amp;test_set_script_id=f36cabd0-32c3-11e0-a61c-52540025f9ae&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=d0b69ab2-c341-11e8-a2b9-52540065bddc&amp;amp;start_date=2026-01-07&amp;amp;end_date=2026-01-07&amp;amp;source=sub_tests#redirect&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/search?client_branch=master&amp;amp;server_branch=master&amp;amp;test_set_script_id=f36cabd0-32c3-11e0-a61c-52540025f9ae&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=d0b69ab2-c341-11e8-a2b9-52540065bddc&amp;amp;start_date=2026-01-07&amp;amp;end_date=2026-01-07&amp;amp;source=sub_tests#redirect&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It isn&apos;t clear looking at the test logs why it is so much slower, but possibly the test is now actually doing what it was &lt;em&gt;supposed&lt;/em&gt; to be doing?  ... or not, but it deserves some investigation.  If the test duration cannot be reduced, then this subtest should be added to the &lt;tt&gt;SLOW&lt;/tt&gt; list.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
